p: Supplementary Figure 1: Phylogenetic analysis of 817 human rhinovirus (HRV) sequences from the Kilifi Health and Demographic Surveillance System (KHDSS) including 1 Coxsackievirus and 2 Enterovirus D68 sequences diagnosed as HRV by PCR. Different species are indicated by different tree branch color; black, HRV species A; red, HRV- species C; blue, HRV species B; pink, EV-D68; green, CV species B. HRV human rhinovirus, EV enterovirus, CV coxsackievirus.
